President Cyril Ramaphosa responds to the Public Protector's questions on the Phala Phala Farm burglary. #DStv403 PRETORIA - President Cyril Ramaphosa has finally responded to the Public Protector's '31 questions' relating to the Phala Phala farm burglary scandal.
The Office is investigating details surrounding the theft of millions in foreign currency in 2020, which was allegedly concealed from police.
Presidency Spokesperson Vincent Magwenya has pledged full cooperation.